{"cacheTime": 1595100747, "baseUrl": "https://kater.me/d/70332", "title": "現在電腦螢幕有技術可以做特定畫面偏振嗎？", "content": [{"author": "桃園阿澤_梗文製造™執行長", "body": "\n<p>\n 就是螢幕顯示正常畫面\n <br/>\n 但是只要有出現特定視窗，那格視窗就會變白，要戴偏振片眼鏡才看得到\n <br/>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JlxVcaY.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JlxVcaY.jpg\" title=\"\"/>\n</a>\n<br/>\n 剛剛想把電腦搬回老家的時候\n <br/>\n 我想到有些東西很怕被我爸媽看到\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "Soro", "body": "\n<p>\n 偏振我還是第一次聽到這名詞\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "桃園阿澤_梗文製造™執行長", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"751306\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/70332/2\">\n Soro\n </a>\n<br/>\n<span data-s9e-mediaembed=\"youtube\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:100%;max-width:640px\">\n<span style=\"display:block;overflow:hidden;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%\">\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Dk9JOd1PY9Y\" style=\"background:url(https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Dk9JOd1PY9Y/hqdefault.jpg) 50% 50% / cover;border:0;height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;width:100%\">\n</iframe>\n</span>\n</span>\n</p>\n"}, {"author": "三十二朔月", "body": "\n<p>\n 現在筆電都OLED的吧\n <br/>\n 玩不了ㄌ\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "frienkie", "body": "\n<p>\n 液晶屏可以自己diy去掉偏光层，好像没有直接卖的\n <br/>\n 还有防窥膜可以减小可视角度\n <br/>\n 但是感觉都还是有些问题\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "frienkie", "body": "\n<p>\n<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av10302504?share_medium=android&amp;share_source=copy_link&amp;bbid=XY7762E7B04C93DA17B9DCB8980686C6C4317&amp;ts=1590940165345\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n http://www.bilibili.com/video/av10302504?share_medium=android&amp;share_source=copy_link&amp;bbid=XY7762E7B04C93DA17B9DCB8980686C6C4317&amp;ts=1590940165345\n </a>\n</p>\n"}, {"author": "桃園阿澤_梗文製造™執行長", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"751444\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/70332/7\">\n frienkie\n </a>\n<br/>\n 這我知道\n <br/>\n 但是我希望是特定畫面偏振\n <br/>\n 螢幕全白一定很可疑嘛\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "frienkie", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"751610\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/70332/8\">\n 桃園阿澤_梗文製造™執行長\n </a>\n 先生，没有那种东西\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "Fruit丨vinegar", "body": "\n<p>\n 透視外掛\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "蔡陰魂還錢", "body": "\n<p>\n 都幾歲了還會煩惱這事= =\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "桃園阿澤_梗文製造™執行長", "body": "\n<p>\n<a class=\"PostMention\" data-id=\"751834\" href=\"https://kater.me/d/70332/11\">\n 蔡陰魂還錢\n </a>\n<br/>\n 這種事情就算娶了老婆也是要防好嗎…\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "Fruit丨vinegar", "body": "\n<p>\n AR 功能好像做的到\n </p>\n<p>\n 別人裸視只會看到一個QRcode的代碼\n </p>\n<p>\n 你用手機相機照可以看到代碼內容\n </p>\n"}, {"author": "可可蘿的頭號大粉絲", "body": "\n<p>\n 窩不知道…\n </p>\n"}]}